### Filament Admin Panels
# Installation
- composer require filament/filament
- php artisan filament:install --panels
- php artisan make:filament-user

### Filament Resources
- php artisan make:filament-resource User
- php artisan make:filament-resource Category --soft-deletes
- php artisan make:filament-resource Course --soft-deletes
- php artisan make:filament-resource CourseMentor --soft-deletes
- php artisan make:filament-resource SectionContent --soft-deletes
- php artisan make:filament-resource Role --soft-deletes
- php artisan make:filament-resource Pricing --soft-deletes
- php artisan make:filament-resource Transaction --soft-deletes

